entries.femaleVariant: Got anything cool for sale?
Anyone can shop here?
Got anything nova for sale?
If you can afford it – yes.
How's this work – any punk off the street can waltz in here, grab some shady-running soft?
But if you come recommended and you know what you are looking for... I am sure you will find it.
No, not just any punk. Over the counter, we fix cyberdecks.
T-Bug sent me to grab a program.
T-Bug sent me. Said you'd have somethin' for me.
Ah, so you are V. I'm sure you heard what happened. Real shame.
You're V, right?
She left a daemon for you. A gift from beyond the grave.
It should work on any third-gen deck.
Got a Militech Paraline. Think it'll do.
Hm, solid gear... for a beginner.
She had me hold a daemon for you.
What do you know about T-Bug's death?
T-Bug's death – what'd you hear?
The truth. She got burned like anyone who tries to hit Arasaka.
They found the body in her pad, nervous system fried. You know what that feels like?
Mh... can't say I do.
They say it's like a hundred thousand knives stabbing you at once. I can't imagine a worse way to go.
Poor girl. I liked her, too.
Always glad to grab a hack.
OK, glad to grab a daemon always.
Got a Militech Paraline…
You could test it now. I have an access point... If you'd like, that is.
You might extract some shim soft or subroutines. Seems worth a try either way...
